类 FilteredMemberList

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Iterable<Symbol>, java.util.Collection<Symbol>, java.util.List<Symbol>

    public class FilteredMemberList
extends java.util.AbstractList<Symbol>
    Utility to construct a view of a symbol's members, filtering out unwanted elements such as synthetic ones. This view is most efficiently accessed through its iterator() method.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.
